snippet.textDisplay: 2019: l learned that if someone is going through a really hard time . tell them you appreciate them and love them . I almost lost my mum because she felt useless  . Luckily I was given another chance to actually say that . It could have been too late . So I guess what I’m trying to say is sometimes people need that reassurance and shouldn’t always assume they already know how we feel.

snippet.textDisplay: I am trying to up my makeup game and also potentially starting a youtube channel because I have been dealing with a lot of academic and financial stress as a low-income/first-generation college student. It was recently my birthday, and I (finally) turned 21, but I did not really get to enjoy it (I was taking finals) and my family somewhat brushed it away, so I felt underwhelmed. I started watching your videos and they were personal and relatable, and you are so unique. That being said, I've never won a giveaway, and it would be an honor to get a gift from you! Thanks for being so kind and generous.
